setResponsibleForSettlement(uint256).notice: Using this function, the Responsible for Settlement indicates that he has made the FIAT money transfer. param redemptionTransactionHash hash of the redeem transaction in which the FIAT money settlement occurred. param receiptHash hash that proof the FIAT money transfer /  function notifyRedemptionSettlement(string memory redemptionTransactionHash, string memory receiptHash) public whenNotPaused onlyResponsibleForSettlement { require (RBBLib.isValidHash(receiptHash), "O hash do recibo é inválido"); emit RedemptionSettlement(redemptionTransactionHash, receiptHash); }
